title: 148: The Costco Haul Episode (June '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Costco Haul Episode (June '21 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the gang are trying some unique finds like spaghetti squash with plant-based Bolognese, pickle-flavored fried cucumbers, birthday cake in a jar, salmon poke, hand-braided cheese, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, not 1, but 2 finds that got a perfect 10 on Lisa’s ratings scale! You want to know which ones? Press play now to find out. Then after the episode, head on over to our Foodcast page for the list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We went back to Costco and found some different and amazing finds on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
